   The Office of Rare Diseases (ORD) is making every effort to ensure that
   the information available on this Web site is accessible to all. If you
   use special adaptive equipment to access the Web and encounter problems
   when using this site, please let us know. Write to: hh70f@nih.gov, send
   us your address, and we will provide the information to you in an
   alternate format. Please be as specific as possible when describing the
   information you seek and the format in which you need to receive it. If
   you prefer to call, our office telephone number is 301-402-4336. Thanks
   for using the ORD Web site.

